{"title":"广场的老人（外一首）","authors":["董雯"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":4,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"广场的老人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"董雯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广场的老人像一尊雕像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个下午"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在阳光里微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞翔的鸽子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔跑的孩子和静物般的老人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的一个下午"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一幅油画挂在城市的中心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个叫街心花园的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像是城市里的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后一方净土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"供人洗涤喧嚣和浮躁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人只是微笑地坐着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直坐到每个人心中的石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都开满了花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵挂你时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常常会觉得疼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种深切的缠绵温柔的疼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论身处何地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起你时就会虔诚地祈祷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把最真实的平安健康"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带给你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时在路边与你分手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟会感到恐慌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在那里看着你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到从我视线走出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像小时候你在路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到看不见的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在望着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道我心疼的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过时空  城市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你正牵挂着我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一轮满月只盈不亏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你知道吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一年我去远方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列车启动的一刹那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你流的那滴泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉沉地  永久地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我心上砸出一个坑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛满了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高尚无私的爱"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}